            <div class="faq-a">PE veterinary acquisitions typically structure transactions with cash up front, multi-year earnouts, rollover equity in the holding entity, and ongoing W-2 employment. We aggregate all three post-sale streams: ongoing W-2 under <a href="https://selling-guide.fanniemae.com/sel/b3-3.1-01/general-income-information" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">B3-3.1-01</a>, rollover equity K-1 under <a href="https://selling-guide.fanniemae.com/sel/b3-3.4-02/analyzing-returns-partnership-or-s-corporation" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">B3-3.4-02</a>, and earnout consideration with multi-year payment schedule documentation. Post-sale qualifying often substantially exceeds pre-sale.</div>
